  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.cactifish_stew.1": "仙人鱼本身没有刺，但人们总认为用它做的炖菜应该有刺，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.cactifish_stew.2": "所以通常会加一份仙人掌，用来符合人们的期待。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.magma_fish_balls": "岩浆鱼丸",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.magma_fish_balls.0": "冒险家会在探索下界前制作的点心。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.magma_fish_balls.1": "虽然做起来很烦，但光凭它的味道就值了！",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.sludge_stew": "污泥炖",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.sludge_stew.0": "用污泥鲶做出的炖菜，看上去很恶心，但尝起来很不错。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.sludge_stew.1": "从沼泽村庄的菜品发展而来，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.sludge_stew.2": "通常是有什么就加什么。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.sludge_stew.3": "用骨勺舀着吃为最佳。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.blossom_toast": "鲜花吐司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.blossom_toast.0": "带有鱼味的吐司，通常用鲜花鱼做成。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.blossom_toast.1": "咬一口就肯定能让你精神百倍，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.blossom_toast.2": "还能向周围的人分享些许樱花味的心绪。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.steamed_redscaled_tuna": "蒸红鳞金枪鱼",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.steamed_redscaled_tuna.0": "蒸制的红鳞金枪鱼，吃了还想吃。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.steamed_redscaled_tuna.1": "绿叶配菜与鱼肉的滋味完美融合，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.steamed_redscaled_tuna.2": "让菜品的层次极为丰富。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.grilled_shroomfish": "烤蘑菇鱼",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.grilled_shroomfish.0": "烤制的蘑菇鱼，配有绿叶蔬菜和马铃薯泥。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.grilled_shroomfish.1": "传言称，这道菜来自一名滞留在蘑菇岛上的水手，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.grilled_shroomfish.2": "几个月来，他只能找到马铃薯和生菜吃。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.spore_nigiri": "孢子握寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.spore_nigiri.0": "使用新鲜（？）孢子鱼制作的独特握寿司。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.spore_nigiri.1": "孢子鱼的气味令人反胃，所以这道菜其实需要多接触才能习惯。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.spore_nigiri.2": "每一口都能让你想起自己正在消化的恶心生态系统。",



  "item.starcatcher_delight.sweet_berry_taiyaki": "甜浆果鲷鱼烧",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.sweet_berry_taiyaki.0": "一份鲷鱼烧，填满了丝滑的甜浆果膏。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.glow_berry_taiyaki": "发光浆果鲷鱼烧",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.glow_berry_taiyaki.0": "用新鲜的发光浆果做成的传统小吃，冒险家在深入深板岩层时会带上一些。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.glow_berry_taiyaki.1": "它能发出淡淡的光，其他人可以在很远的地方发现它。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.chocolate_taiyaki": "巧克力鲷鱼烧",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.chocolate_taiyaki.0": "巧克力馅鲷鱼烧，常用来奖励乖孩子。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.honey_taiyaki": "蜂蜜鲷鱼烧",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.honey_taiyaki.0": "这种鲷鱼烧传统上由养蜂人制作，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.honey_taiyaki.1": "常在向旅行者出售蜂蜜时用作附礼。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.pumpkin_taiyaki": "南瓜鲷鱼烧",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.pumpkin_taiyaki.0": "最常见的鲷鱼烧。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.pumpkin_taiyaki.1": "甜蜜、柔软、不干涩，是小吃中的极佳之选。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.watermelon_taiyaki": "西瓜鲷鱼烧",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.watermelon_taiyaki.0": "这种鲷鱼烧常见于丛林周围，里面填着西瓜膏，味道很是清新。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.suspicious_taiyaki": "鲷鱼烧？",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.suspicious_taiyaki.0": "长得像鲷鱼烧的……某种东西……",






  "item.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet": "捕星鱼排",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet.0": "§7一份<未知品质>的鱼排",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_common": "捕星鱼排",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_common.0": "一片生鱼排，闻上去跟快坏了一样。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_uncommon": "捕星鱼排",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_uncommon.0": "鱼肉料理的主要原料。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_rare": "捕星鱼排",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_rare.0": "看上去很不错的鱼排。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_rare.1": "无论用它做什么，都一定会是高品质的菜肴。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_epic": "捕星鱼排",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_epic.0": "质量优秀的鱼排。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_epic.1": "用它创造出的菜品定能让人心向往之。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_legendary": "捕星鱼排",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_legendary.0": "极为珍贵的鱼排，取自<sclegendary>传说</sclegendary>品质的鱼。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.starcaught_fillet_legendary.1": "把它切成鱼排都算暴殄天物，但你总不禁想象，用它做成的菜品究竟能有多美味。",





  "item.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki": "细卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki.0": "§7一枚<未知品质>的细卷寿司",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_common": "细卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_common.0": "试作型细卷寿司。米粒散得到处都是，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_common.1": "鱼肉有种烂掉的怪味。相当恶心。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_uncommon": "细卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_uncommon.0": "从长条寿司卷上切下的一枚细卷寿司。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_uncommon.1": "吃起来平淡乏味，大概是因为用了鱼身上最差的部位；",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_uncommon.2": "不管如何，你也只能这样安慰自己了。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_rare": "细卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_rare.0": "用新鲜鱼肉做成的一枚细卷寿司，味道不错。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_rare.1": "此等品质的寿司，已能算是半步踏入奢华美食的大门了。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_epic": "细卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_epic.0": "高品质寿司的完美样例。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_epic.1": "轻轻咬上一口，就足以把你带向欢欣的殿堂，让你",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_epic.2": "吃下一枚还想要一枚，直到消灭完整条寿司卷才算停。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_legendary": "细卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_legendary.0": "绝美的鱼肉佳肴，是其他菜品只敢想见的完美化身。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_legendary.1": "即便是最为挑剔的食客，也会拜倒在这枚寿司之前，想着能否再来一枚。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.hosomaki_legendary.2": "但麻烦的是，等到你品尝完之后，可就没有能留给他们的了。",





  "item.starcatcher_delight.nigiri": "握寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri.0": "§7一个<未知品质>的握寿司",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_common": "握寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_common.0": "一个恶心的握寿司。看上去快散架了。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_common.1": "看一眼鱼肉的颜色就能打消胃口。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_uncommon": "握寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_uncommon.0": "学徒学做的握寿司。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_uncommon.1": "尽管鱼肉不是优品，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_uncommon.2": "当作零食也算不错。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_rare": "握寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_rare.0": "制作精良的握寿司，口感松软的米饭上放着新鲜的鱼肉。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_rare.1": "是为味蕾准备的大餐。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_epic": "握寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_epic.0": "外观极为优雅的握寿司。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_epic.1": "米粒看上去让人食欲大振，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_epic.2": "菜品整体的美观更是让人食指大动。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_legendary": "握寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_legendary.0": "这类寿司做起来并不复杂，",
