  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.nigiri_legendary.3": "它发出的香味引得人口齿生津，就差品味一番了。",





  "item.starcatcher_delight.temaki": "手卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki.0": "§7<未知品质>的手卷寿司",

