  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_common.0": "相当恶心的手卷寿司。米粒争着从海苔筒里逃走，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_common.1": "却又被鱼肉的腥味拉住。好恶心。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.temaki_uncommon": "手卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_uncommon.0": "试作型手卷寿司，很明显是新手做的。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_uncommon.1": "鱼肉质量差，寿司质量也就差。没什么可说的了。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.temaki_rare": "手卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_rare.0": "仔细卷起的手卷寿司，鱼肉品质不错。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_rare.1": "每一口下去，都是口感和口味的完美平衡，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_rare.2": "是相当好吃的小点心。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.temaki_epic": "手卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_epic.0": "精美的手卷寿司，制作手法精湛。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_epic.1": "海苔被卷成完美的锥形，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_epic.2": "配料的滋味浓郁而丰富，余韵久久不散。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.temaki_legendary": "手卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_legendary.0": "这份手卷寿司超脱于简单餐食之上，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_legendary.1": "每一种原料均为优中选优、万里挑一，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_legendary.2": "它们相辅相成，和谐得有种不真实感。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.temaki_legendary.3": "仅是一口，就足以让你相信，世上真的存在完美的事物。",






  "item.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_common": "反卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_common.0": "卷得歪七扭八的反卷寿司。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_common.1": "米团干燥，而且表面坑坑洼洼，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_common.2": "里面的配料更是会在下口之前就散架。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_uncommon": "反卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_uncommon.0": "初学者制作的反卷寿司，只是堪堪能过关。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_uncommon.1": "能吃，但口感不太好，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_uncommon.2": "不过即便它没什么味道，也依然能填饱肚子。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_rare": "反卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_rare.0": "卷得整整齐齐的反卷寿司，里面裹着一片新鲜的鱼肉。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_rare.1": "米饭和鱼肉相得益彰，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_rare.2": "口味均衡，能带来满足感。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_epic": "反卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_epic.0": "精致的反卷寿司，是厨师纯熟手艺的体现。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_epic.1": "每一粒米的调味都恰到好处，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_epic.2": "更衬托出配料的新鲜风味。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_legendary": "反卷寿司",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_legendary.0": "这份反卷寿司即是优异厨艺的化身。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_legendary.1": "各种配料依次裹起，将丰富的滋味包在内部，又在口中接连迸发，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_legendary.2": "每一层都加上了全新的层次。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.uramaki_legendary.3": "好像在吃的不是一道餐点，而是值得铭记的一次体验。",






  "item.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad": "鱼肉沙拉",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad.0": "§7<未知品质>的鱼肉沙拉",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_common": "鱼肉沙拉",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_common.0": "淡而无味的鱼肉沙拉。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_uncommon": "鱼肉沙拉",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_uncommon.0": "随手拌成的鱼肉沙拉，和鱼片的品质也算匹配。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_rare": "鱼肉沙拉",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_rare.0": "拌得相当精细的鱼肉沙拉。外观亮眼，味道可口。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_epic": "鱼肉沙拉",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_epic.0": "这碗沙拉的酱料裹得非常均匀，如同薄纱拂面。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_epic.1": "无论如何，它都足够管你好一会的饱了。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_legendary": "鱼肉沙拉",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_legendary.0": "你见过最能激发食欲的鱼肉沙拉。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_legendary.1": "从分量到外观，一切都是那么完美。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_legendary.2": "只是看一眼，就让你口中泛起唾液，想着上去吃一口了。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.fish_salad_legendary.3": "抓紧吧，不然沙拉就被抢完啦！",








  "item.starcatcher_delight.healthy_fish_omelette": "健康鱼肉煎蛋卷",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.healthy_fish_omelette.0": "§7<未知品质>的健康鱼肉煎蛋卷",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.healthy_fish_omelette_common": "健康鱼肉煎蛋卷",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.healthy_fish_omelette_common.0": "蛋还是生的，鱼也没熟，蔬菜更是像块纸板。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.healthy_fish_omelette_common.1": "吞下这份试作型食物带来的痛苦已非言语所能形容。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.healthy_fish_omelette_uncommon": "健康鱼肉煎蛋卷",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.healthy_fish_omelette_uncommon.0": "管它叫“健康”其实稍微夸大了点，",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.healthy_fish_omelette_uncommon.1": "不过它也确实有些份量，能稍稍填饱肚子。",

  "item.starcatcher_delight.healthy_fish_omelette_rare": "健康鱼肉煎蛋卷",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.healthy_fish_omelette_rare.0": "好吃的煎蛋卷，里面点缀着鱼肉丁。",
  "tooltip.starcatcher_delight.healthy_fish_omelette_rare.1": "选材很独特，但合在一起反倒还挺不错的。",

